{"id":75,"date":"2025-07-21T18:36:23","date_gmt":"2025-07-21T18:36:23","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/callmedley.com\/?post_type=services&#038;p=75"},"modified":"2025-07-28T00:09:06","modified_gmt":"2025-07-28T00:09:06","slug":"attic-insulation","status":"publish","type":"services","link":"https:\/\/callmedley.com\/services\/attic-insulation\/","title":{"rendered":"Attic Insulation"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.callmedley.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/Frame.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-332\"\/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h1 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Carrolton, TX Attic Insulation<\/h1>\n\n\n\n<p>Did you know that insulating your attic can save you money and keep you more comfortable all year round? That\u2019s right! Attic insulation isn\u2019t just right for people in cold climates. It can help you live better at home no matter where you live.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Save Money<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Attic insulation helps you save money by saving energy. When your attic is insulated, less of the cold or hot air that you\u2019re pumping into your house will escape. This means that your heating and air conditioning won\u2019t have to work as hard. When they\u2019re getting a break, you\u2019re not using as much energy and, when you\u2019re not using as much energy, your energy costs will go down.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>You may also save money with attic insulation because you may not have to replace your heater and air conditioner as often. When they aren\u2019t working as hard, they won\u2019t sustain as much wear and tear. Since this eventually leads to damage, they may well last longer simply because you insulated your Carrollton attic.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Stay Comfortable<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Insulating your attic can help you stay more comfortable because it doesn\u2019t let as much air escape. That extra layer can mean you stay cooler in the summer and warmer in the winter, all while using less energy. If you get cold at home or you feel like your comfort systems are always working overtime and barely hanging on, insulating your attic could be the solution you\u2019ve been looking for.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Our Process<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Our Carrollton attic insulation team will come out and assess your current insulation situation. Insulation is rated based on an R-value. Different types of insulation have different R-values per inch. We know what your target R-value should be and we\u2019ll be able to tell you whether or not you\u2019re hitting it. These targets are based on optimizing your home for energy efficiency without overspending on insulation.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you\u2019re not hitting your target R-value, we\u2019ll devise a solution to get you there. We may need to tear out your old insulation, or we might simply be able to add to it so you can retain hot and cold air better.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Once we have a plan, we\u2019ll get to work and have your attic insulation done fast. We always wear appropriate protection while we work, and we\u2019ll strive to protect you and your family, too. Some types of insulation can damage your lungs, but we won\u2019t let that happen. When we\u2019re done, your home\u2019s indoor temperatures should be more stable and your utility bills should go down.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We\u2019ll find a solution that works for you, then get it implemented quickly so you don\u2019t waste your money anymore!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"tel:4698874874\"><strong>Give us a call at (469) 887-4874<\/strong><\/a><strong>&nbsp;or&nbsp;<\/strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.callmedley.com\/contact-us\/\"><strong>contact us online<\/strong><\/a><strong>&nbsp;today to request service for attic insulation in Carrollton.&nbsp;<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Further Reading:<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.callmedley.com\/b